	Craig chest    
	 London, Sept. 5 (PTI): James Bond star Daniel Craig has topped an online poll to emerge as the man with the best male chest, beating the likes of Brad Pitt and Gerard Butler.       
	The 41-year-old actors bare-chested appearance in a scene from Casino Royale has secured his position at the top with 34 per cent votes, the Sun has reported online.       
	Butler won the second place for his eight-packed appearance in the Spartan epic 300. Brad Pitt came third for Troy, in the survey conducted by Lovefilm.com.      
	Former Bond star Sean Connery bagged the fifth place with his bare-chested act in Thunderball, while Leonardo DiCaprio came sixth for his film The Beach.                                                                                                                                                                       
